Package: sspLNIRT
Title: Sample Size Planning for Joint Hierarchical Modelling using LNIRT
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sebastian A. J.", "Lortz", , "s.a.j.lortz@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Sample size planning tools for the Joint Hierarchical Model 
    using a 2-PL normal ogive model for response accuracy and a 3-PL 
    log-normal model for response time, estimated via the LNIRT package.
